      • getDownstreamPortType

        public PortType getDownstreamPortType(int index)
        Used in FromFileNodeContainerPersistor.guessPortTypesFromConnectedNodes( NodeAndBundleInformation, NodeSettingsRO, ArrayList, ArrayList) to retrieve the port types of up- and downstream nodes. Might return null (if this node is missing, too).
